&lt;blockquote class=&#34;alert alert-note&#34;&gt;















    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;前言：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;个人喜好问题，软件的安装不喜欢用exe安装，更喜欢用压缩包形式进行安装，这样方便管理，也方便卸载&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;所以下面的python也是以压缩包形式进行搭建，也就是&lt;strong&gt;免安装&lt;/strong&gt;或&lt;strong&gt;绿色版&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-python安装&#34;&gt;1 Python安装
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(1) 前往&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.python.org/downloads/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;strong&gt;Python官网&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;，选择要下载的版本，点击对应的download&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1350&#34;
	height=&#34;535&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD1_hu5555568738207442362.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD1_hu15234259659145039565.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;252&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;605px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(2) 点击下载对应电脑位数的&lt;strong&gt;Windows embeddable package&lt;/strong&gt;包&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1340&#34;
	height=&#34;504&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD2_hu669687186614799334.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD2_hu5339246725101096413.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;265&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;638px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(3) 下载完后直接解压&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;875&#34;
	height=&#34;483&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD3_hu3177232495211463377.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD3_hu9455462449350410125.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;181&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;434px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(4) 配置环境变量
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;此电脑&lt;/code&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;code&gt;鼠标右键&lt;/code&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;code&gt;属性&lt;/code&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;code&gt;高级系统设置&lt;/code&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;code&gt;环境变量&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;将python文件夹路径加入到&lt;strong&gt;path&lt;/strong&gt;中&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1271&#34;
	height=&#34;656&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE1_hu6923260931511668893.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE1_hu12057450863988303937.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;193&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;465px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;527&#34;
	height=&#34;563&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE2_hu16328763852489462966.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE2_hu15698168266117394990.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;93&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;224px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(5) 打开命令行，输入&lt;code&gt;python -V&lt;/code&gt;，正常显示版本号则安装成功&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/python%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95.png&#34;
