	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;254&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;611px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-pip安装&#34;&gt;2 Pip安装
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote class=&#34;alert alert-tip&#34;&gt;















    &lt;p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;pip&lt;/strong&gt;是Python官方提供的包管理工具，用于安装Python第三方库，&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;pip&lt;/strong&gt;安装包后，可以不用再下载安装包，直接使用命令行安装，方便管理，也方便卸载&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;所以搭建python环境基本都要安装pip&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(1) 前往&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://pypi.org/project/pip/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pypi&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;，下载&lt;strong&gt;get-pip.py&lt;/strong&gt;文件(&lt;kbd&gt;Ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;+&lt;kbd&gt;S&lt;/kbd&gt;保存)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;上方标签可查看支持的python版本&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD.png&#34;
	width=&#34;944&#34;
	height=&#34;659&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu12648631603669106140.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu6569780432046611905.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;143&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;343px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;917&#34;
	height=&#34;554&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD2_hu11489025882399472246.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD2_hu1136306123010289467.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;165&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;397px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(2) 下载后放入python文件夹，打开命令行运行&lt;code&gt;python get-pip.py&lt;/code&gt;安装&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85.png&#34;
	width=&#34;929&#34;
	height=&#34;340&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85_hu17564093063608403168.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85_hu5619660392491308176.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;273&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;655px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(3) 修改&lt;strong&gt;python312._pth&lt;/strong&gt;，将&lt;code&gt;import site&lt;/code&gt;的注释去掉，允许Python加载&lt;strong&gt;site-packages&lt;/strong&gt;目录
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;不同版本文件名中的数字不一致，按自己实际情况修改对应的&lt;strong&gt;pth&lt;/strong&gt;文件&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%852.png&#34;
	width=&#34;663&#34;
	height=&#34;455&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%852_hu5387804586641296204.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%852_hu5148449657674300684.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;145&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;349px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(4) 将安装pip产生的&lt;strong&gt;Scripts&lt;/strong&gt;文件夹加入到环境变量中(参考python安装)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.png&#34;
	width=&#34;949&#34;
	height=&#34;568&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE_hu11309827044125026175.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE_hu10221373135494075502.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;400px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;(5) 打开命令行输入&lt;code&gt;pip -V&lt;/code&gt;，正常显示版本号则安装成功&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95.png&#34;
	width=&#34;861&#34;
	height=&#34;195&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95_hu8876805099299470519.png 480w, https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/python/build-env/pip%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95_hu1958704254797024362.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;441&#34;
